---
title: Falafel Mezze Bowl with Honey Roasted Aubergine and Zhoug Couscous
description: Hailing from Middle Eastern and Levantine cuisine, falafel are a fast favourite with vegetarians and meat-eaters alike due to their unique texture and versatile flavour. Our Falafel Mezze Bowl takes inspiration from the best of hot mezze dishes to make a vibrant dish.
